+# Flask Currency Converter
+
+A small Flask app that converts an entered amount between a fixed list of currencies using hard-coded exchange rates.
+
+## Run locally
+
+Install dependencies:
+
+```bash
+pip install -r requirements.txt
+```
+
+Start the app on port 5017:
+
+```bash
+python app.py
+```
+
+Open `http://127.0.0.1:5017` in your browser.
