The app runs on port `5019`, compares two textareas with line-by-line additions/removals, includes CSRF protection, Argon2 password hashing for optional accounts, parameterized SQLite queries, access control for saved comparisons, secure headers, environment-based secrets, and generic error pages.

Per the provided working agreement, I did not install dependencies, run, serve, build, or test the application.
