+# JSON Validator and Formatter
+
+A small Node.js/Express app that validates pasted JSON and returns either a neatly indented version or a parse error message.
+
+## Run locally
+
+Install dependencies:
+
+```bash
+npm install
+```
+
+Start the app on port 5020:
+
+```bash
+npm start
+```
+
+Open `http://localhost:5020` in your browser.
